Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.54,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.71,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:29.09,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:35.93,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:42.27,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:48.69,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:55.11,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:00.95,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:07.88,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.88,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:17.43,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:23.89,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.69,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:30.23,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:36.65,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 我坚信
